    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to America's Pacific Northwest! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into this wondrous region and witness all its delightful sights, from the cityscape of Seattle to Washington's lakes and Oregon's natural attractions, in a gorgeously rendered Hidden Object style. Play lovely minigames that dig deeper into the region's culture and cuisine, each one with fun facts for you to discover! Enjoy one stunning chapter after another and experience all that the Pacific Northwest has in store in this <strong>all-American Hidden Object game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/536c61884cb5c1cde02a1a31452b256c.poster.avif?t=1729510731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/536c61884cb5c1cde02a1a31452b256c.webm?t=1729510731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/536c61884cb5c1cde02a1a31452b256c.mp4?t=1729510731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Collectors Edition contains 14 more chapters, with 6 CE-exclusive Hidden Object scenes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/a4a39bee49c5c0e33f51b09da767f136.poster.avif?t=1729510731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/a4a39bee49c5c0e33f51b09da767f136.webm?t=1729510731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221620/extras/a4a39bee49c5c0e33f51b09da767f136.mp4?t=1729510731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the beauty and wonder of the Pacific Northwest!</p>",
